tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE MentorshipProgram (
    mentor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    mentor_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    mentor_email VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    mentor_interests TEXT,
    mentor_skills TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Mentees (
    mentee_id INT,
    mentee_name VARCHAR(50),
    mentee_interests TEXT,
    mentee_experience_years INT,
    mentor_preferences TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE MentorshipMatches (
    match_id INT,
    mentor_id INT,
    mentee_id INT,
    match_score FLOAT,
    match_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE compatibility (
    mentor_id INTEGER,
    mentee_id INTEGER,
    score INTEGER,
    PRIMARY KEY (mentor_id, mentee_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (mentor_id) REFERENCES mentors(mentor_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (mentee_id) REFERENCES mentees(mentee_id)
);

CREATE TABLE mentor_interests (
    mentor_id INTEGER,
    interest_id INTEGER,
    PRIMARY KEY (mentor_id, interest_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (mentor_id) REFERENCES mentors(mentor_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (interest_id) REFERENCES interests(interest_id)
);
